data.rationale:
This module provides one way of data storage and management in
    BIE(Biological Integrated Environments). It will implement
    interfaces to important data type, e.g. table, in HDF5.
    PDL::IO::HDF5 is bind tightly with PDL and right now it only
    supports simple data types in HDF5.
